  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="MTA13">
<l>iyalvāka vīṉṟuḻā yāṉaṭikkē cella</l>
<l>muyalvā riyalamarar muṉṉa – miyalvāka</l>
<l>nītiyā lōti niyamaṅka ḷālparava</l>
<l>vātiyāy niṉṟā ravar</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>While the immortals by nature, who make an effort</l>
<l>to go to the feet of him with naturally lush tulsi,</l>
<l>recite according to the rule, as is natural, [and] revere through observances,</l>
<l>he stands [there] as the beginning.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
